OL,3,CWoman, 55, killed and man injured
OL,4,Cafter motorcycles and car crash
OL,6,FA female motorcyclist has died and
OL,7,Fanother man has been injured in a
OL,8,Fcollision in West Sussex involving two
OL,9,Fbikes and a car.
OL,11,FThe 55-year-old woman from Bognor was
OL,12,Fpronounced dead at the scene of the
OL,13,Fcrash in Ford Road, Ford, next to
OL,14,FNelson Row.
OL,16,FHer next of kin has been informed.
OL,18,FThe accident happened at about midday
OL,19,Fon Saturday, May 23rd.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
