OL,3,CWoman, 55, killed and man injured
OL,4,Cafter motorcycles and car crash
OL,6,FThe rider of a second motorcycle, a 57-
OL,7,Fyear-old man from Bognor, also
OL,8,Fsustained injuries.
OL,10,FThe driver of a white Mini, a 60-year-
OL,11,Fold man from Angmering, was not
OL,12,Finjured.
OL,14,FSussex Police are investigating the
OL,15,Fcircumstances of the collision.
